content.html: The pandemic changed us all. I guess I’m still coming to terms with evolving *from here* instead of desperately trying to return to who I was before and “pick up where I left off.” It’s ok if that process is tiny baby steps. Concluding this 🧵 w/ some good travel memories. 🌎✈️
